**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

.git
.github
.claude
.vscode
.idea

# apps/web and tests/e2e aren't built into this image, but their package.json files
# are still COPYed (see Dockerfile) so `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` sees the full
# workspace member set the lockfile expects. Don't blanket-exclude their directories —
# Docker can't un-exclude a file whose parent directory was already excluded.
apps/web/.next
apps/web/src
tests/e2e/test-results
tests/e2e/playwright-report
tests/e2e/.cache

*.md
!README.md
